            <i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up feature-icon mb-4" style="font-size: 4rem; color: white;"></i>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-white" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">Easy Setup</h5>
            <p class="text-white" style="font-size: 1rem;">Quickly create and host Tambola games with our intuitive
